channel.title: Need Help with Server
channel.description:
Hi I can't seem to get my private server to let others connect. I have utorrent and no-ip set up. I changed the ip of the client. I feel like everything is right and the server still doesn't work. I just changed one thing and I would like somebody to try and connect to it. If you have teamviewer it would be helpful too because you might be able to find the problem for me. PM me if you can help.
The source I used is Project Amaze made by omgitsshane. Also, I can connect to my server its just that others can't.

item.title: Need Help with Server
item.dc:creator: @Jeffrey7 Jeffrey7
item.description:
@Jeffrey7 wrote:

I followed those guides and the guide on portforward.com. Heres what I put in.
Local ip: 0
Internal Port: 43594
Public Interface ip: 0.0.0.0
Ext Start Port: 43594
Ext End Port: 43594
Protocol: Both
Enabled box is checked.

If anyone can, please help with teamviewer.
